♪ contemplative piano music ♪

26:40.917 --> 26:43.792
♪♪♪

26:46.166 --> 26:49.000
Fine.

26:54.542 --> 26:57.291
[exasperated sigh]

26:57.291 --> 27:03.166
♪♪♪

27:16.375 --> 27:19.500
[waves crashing]

28:24.000 --> 28:26.834
[Matt sniffling]

28:33.375 --> 28:34.667
Fucker!

28:34.667 --> 28:35.709
Ugh!

28:42.041 --> 28:43.583
Ugh!

28:45.417 --> 28:46.500
Ugh!

